Passant
=======

A small ruby library for chess experiments.


Example
=======

Requires are relative to lib/ so you have to add it to your load path one way or another.

[running irb under lib/]

irb(main):001:0> require 'passant/board'
=> true
irb(main):002:0> b = Passant::Board.new
=> 
rnbqkbnr
pppppppp
........
........
........
........
PPPPPPPP
RNBQKBNR
irb(main):003:0> b.move(a2,a4)
=> Pa2a4
irb(main):004:0> b
=> 
rnbqkbnr
pppppppp
........
........
P.......
........
.PPPPPPP
RNBQKBNR
irb(main):005:0> 
